373
00:39:41.922 --> 00:39:43.716
Bagus sekali. Siapa namanya?

374
00:39:45.174 --> 00:39:46.509
Nama?

375
00:39:48.553 --> 00:39:51.096
- Scott dan Leslie.
- Scott dan Leslie.


376
00:39:58.186 --> 00:40:00.940
- Itu Audry.
