378
00:40:04.443 --> 00:40:07.030
Hai, Audry. Ya Tuhan.

379
00:40:08.698 --> 00:40:10.115
- Hai.
- Hai, Audry.


380
00:40:10.282 --> 00:40:12.451
- Lihat siapa yang ada di sini.
- Hai, Audry.


381
00:40:12.910 --> 00:40:15.453
- Apa kabar?
- Senang berjumpa denganmu.


382
00:40:52.114 --> 00:40:54.075
Semuanya berteriak!

383
00:40:57.619 --> 00:40:59.328
