467
00:47:52.639 --> 00:47:55.310
Kau sepertinya tertarik
dengan aku dan Audry.


468
00:47:56.519 --> 00:47:57.978
Kami teman lama.

469
00:48:07.862 --> 00:48:11.325
Bisa aku minta minuman bersoda?
Bisakah kau?


470
00:48:11.574 --> 00:48:12.825
- Charlie?
